full_text: @WilliamsonNFL Here's a plot for all thee variables: (1) completion% (x-axis), (2) aDOT (y-axis), (3) aDOT time completion% (the contours).  Up and to the right is improvement.  Example: Tua and Trevor Lawrence similar by the metric (on the 4.8 yd contour), much different approaches. #nflverse https://t.co/jvHTy7lwcg
